# Build Verification

- Do not run `npm run build` after every change by default.
- Run lightweight checks such as lint/type diagnostics when useful.
- Only run production builds when the user explicitly asks for a build, release check, deployment check, or says to verify with build.
- If a change is risky and a build would normally be prudent, ask before running it.
